data.description: Walking in the door your breath is taken away with stunning views of the Pungo River and the Intra Coastal Waterway.  You are minutes away by boat or car to dining and shopping in downtown Belhaven. Enjoy your paddle board, kayak and other water toys right from your own pier! A firepit and double swing face the water as well.  A fenced in area in the back yard just off the TV room offers space for pets and children to play safely away from the water. The Ellis Cove community has a boat launch and pier, private road, and no HOA. Upgraded features include a gas fireplace, an outdoor fountain, a deep custom tub and tiled shower in the master bath, windows (2020), and some light fixtures. The spacious kitchen opens to the dining and living area with bamboo flooring, granite countertops and ample storage. The master suite, additional bedrooms, and 2nd full bath are all located on the first/lower level. Upstairs is a bonus/flex room/area with two large closets. This room is perfect for gaming, relaxation, or a home office. Separate laundry room just off the kitchen with extra cabinet space, large sink and access to the exterior. The front yard features a large, detached outbuilding (25x40) for your cars, bike and workshop. It has concrete floors with water and electricity. The building also has an attached 12-foot open carport. Seller is offering a one-year home warranty not to exceed $500.  Square footage to be verified by Buyers Agent.
